    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Cryptopontius expletus sp. nov., female holotype (MNRJ 12912). (a) habitus, dorsal view; (b) urosomites 2 – 5, dorsal; (c) antennule; (d) antenna; (e) distal end of mandibular stylet. Scale bars: a = 250 µm; b – c = 100 µm; d – e = 25 µm." ;
