<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.184862>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Cryptopontius expletus sp. nov., female holotype (MNRJ 12912). (a) maxillule; (b) maxilla; (c) maxilliped; (d) P 1; (e) P 2. Scale bars: a = 25 µm; b – e = 100 µm." ;
